# Privacy Policy for Grapevne

Last Updated: [Current Date]

## 1. Information We Collect

### 1.1 Information You Provide
- Account information (email address, username)
- Profile information (emoji, profile picture)
- Content you post (food photos, descriptions, locations)
- Dietary preferences and tags
- School affiliation

### 1.2 Information We Collect Automatically
- Device information (device ID, FCM token for notifications)
- Location data (to show food items near you)
- Usage data (interactions with posts, notifications)
- Photos (when you choose to share food images)

### 1.3 Information from Third Parties
- Firebase Authentication data
- School-specific information

## 2. How We Use Your Information

### 2.1 To Provide Our Services
- Display and manage food posts
- Show relevant food items on the map
- Send notifications about new posts and interactions
- Manage user connections and following
- Handle dietary preference filtering

### 2.2 To Improve Our Services
- Analyze app usage patterns
- Improve user experience
- Develop new features
- Maintain app security

### 2.3 To Communicate With You
- Send notifications about:
  - New food posts
  - Post expirations
  - Saved post updates
  - User interactions
  - System updates

## 3. Information Sharing

### 3.1 With Other Users
- Your posts are visible to other users
- Your username and profile picture are visible
- Your location data is shared when you post

### 3.2 With Service Providers
- Firebase (authentication, database, storage)
- Apple (push notifications, maps)

### 3.3 Legal Requirements
We may share information if required by law or to protect our rights.

## 4. Your Choices

### 4.1 Account Information
- You can update your profile information
- You can delete your account
- You can control notification preferences

### 4.2 Location Data
- You can control location permissions
- You can disable location services

### 4.3 Notifications
- You can manage notification preferences
- You can disable specific notification types
- You can opt out of all notifications

## 5. Data Security
- We use Firebase security rules
- We implement authentication measures
- We protect user data in transit and at rest

## 6. Data Retention
- We retain your data as long as your account is active
- You can request data deletion
- Some data may be retained for legal purposes

## 7. Children's Privacy
This app is not intended for users under 13 years of age.

## 8. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy. We will notify you of any material changes.

## 9. Contact Us
For privacy-related questions, contact us at [Your Contact Information]
